text: Queen is the debut studio album by Queen and was released on 13 July 1973 by EMI Records in the United Kingdom and by Elektra Records in the United States. It went to number 32 in the United Kingdom, number 52 in Japan and number 83 in the United States. == Track listing == === Original release === All lead vocals by Freddie Mercury unless noted. === 2011 Universal Music reissue === === iTunes deluxe edition (2011) === == References == Category:1973 albums Category:Debut albums Category:Queen (band) albums Category:Elektra Records albums
title: Queen (album)
